Dependencies:
wget
xdeb
gawk
sed
w3m

Installation:
git clone https://github.com/poach3r/sift/
chmod +x ~/sift/sift.sh
sudo mv ~/sift/sift.sh /usr/bin

Usage:
sudo sift.sh [PACKAGE]

To change mirror location, modify line 4.

Plans:
1. Notify user when theres no packages found instead of displaying random $$$$
2. Create an actual command
3. Easy Mirror Changing
4. Non-Free repo access
